content: I actually have the receipts from the past few weeks, and I've been trying to keep track of my spending. Let me see... I think I spent around $120 at Walmart last Sunday, $50 at Trader Joe's the week before, $80 with Instacart earlier this month, and $15 on almonds from Costco last month. I also spent $20 on ingredients for lentil soup at the Indian grocery store last week.
